column10:
this game is a masterpiece of turn base strategy. however, i don't like the attitude of sid & comp. who constantly mock their players :
- this game treats the history of mankind as a game of chess, where a quick victory is rewarded and a hard worked victory is consider "shamefull" by the high score list;
- the a.i. is programmed to harass and backstabb the human players. even after 10 years of "dealing" with the civilisation francise i still got trolled by an a.i. player (on the lowest difficulty !!!) - who used a slip away moment to steal my hard worked space race victory :P
